- When ingesting new NarrativeEvent data (via API or ingestion pipeline), the system validates payload structure, stores in NarrativeEvent table, and updates provenance/audit logs.

8) Audit & Export (Optional)
- Admin can inspect provenance for each event and export audit artifacts if required.

